    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利称特朗普胜选几率上升将提振美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/rising-odds-of-a-trump-win-to-boost-dollar-morgan-stanley-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利分析师表示，今年晚些时候共和党当选总统的可能性增加，即便共和党试图抵消美元的强势，但仍将提振美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/rising-odds-of-a-trump-win-to-boost-dollar-morgan-stanley-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 20:09:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波动性为私募股权投资带来机遇：Patricia Miller Zollar</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-06/volatility-offers-opportunity-for-pe-patricia-miller-zollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在约 6.5 万亿美元的抛售震动全球市场之后，新一波逢低买入刺激股市反弹。
标普 500 指数所有主要成分股均上涨，该指数有望创下 2 月份以来的最大涨幅。Neuberger Berman 的 Patricia Miller Zollar 在“彭博市场”节目中与 Scarlet Fu 和 Sonali Basak 谈论了私人市场如何受到公开市场波动的影响。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-06/volatility-offers-opportunity-for-pe-patricia-miller-zollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 20:08:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Airbnb 因前景疲软而暴跌，表明美国需求放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/airbnb-gives-soft-outlook-on-signs-of-slowing-demand-from-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Airbnb Inc. 连续第三个季度发布令人失望的业绩展望，并警告美国游客需求放缓，随后其股价大幅下跌 — — 这表明，即使在夏季旅游旺季，旅游支出势头也将继续减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/airbnb-gives-soft-outlook-on-signs-of-slowing-demand-from-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 20:04:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佛罗里达州新兴城市借款修复被飓风摧毁的码头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/rich-florida-boomtown-borrows-to-fix-pier-wiped-out-by-hurricane</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佛罗里达州那不勒斯正在利用市政债券市场来重建遭飓风伊恩摧毁的著名码头，这已是该市因极端天气破坏而进行的至少第五次重建。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/rich-florida-boomtown-borrows-to-fix-pier-wiped-out-by-hurricane</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 17:15:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
